Q: Guess the output: ConcurrentModificationException

```java
List<String> list = new ArrayList<>(Arrays.asList("A", "B", "C"));
for (String s : list) {
    if (s.equals("B")) {
        list.remove(s);
    }
}
System.out.println(list);
```

